<refsect1 id="accerciser-1-desc"><title>&desc-tt;</title>
<para>&cmd; is an interactive Python accessibility explorer for the GNOME
desktop. It uses AT-SPI to inspect and control widgets, allowing you to
check if an application is providing correct information to assistive
technologies and automated test frameworks. &cmd; has a simple
plug-in framework which you can use to create custom views of
accessibility information.
</para>
</refsect1>
